3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes a new algorithm for solving optimization problems, which falls under the domain of data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes an optimization algorithm that can be used in various AI applications, such as training neural networks.
